<title>Change fullscreen background color</title>

<p>If you like, you can change the background color in fullscreen mode.</p>

<p>To do this, make sure that <link xref="plugins">eog-plugins</link> is
installed. Then, click <guiseq><gui>Edit</gui><gui>Preferences</gui></guiseq> and 
go to the <gui>Plugins</gui> tab. Then, check <gui>Fullscreen Background</gui> and click <gui>Preferences</gui>. Choose the color you want in fullscreen mode and click <gui>Close</gui></p>

<p>Now, when in fullscreen mode, the background color is the one you selected.</p>

